                    whose details have been received.
                </p>

                <p>
                    <b>2. AGREEMENT:</b>
                    This is a legally binding document that will come into force between the applicant and Motion Inc.
                    Sports on the basis of these terms and conditions. Upon entering into this agreement the applicant                   and Motion Inc. Sports will be bound by the disciplines, rules and customs of the academy. The applicant’s
