                    A sign up fee of R2000.00 for a team registration is payable on submission of your application form.
                    <b>This will not be refunded under any circumstances.</b>
                </p>

                <p>
                    <b>4. SUSPENSION AND PERMANENT EXCLUSION:</b>
                    In the event that fees are not paid, Motion Inc. Sports reserves the right to suspend the
                    team from the current league and if seen necessary, permanent exclusion of the applicant from participating in
                    future league events may apply.
                </p>

                <p>
                    <b>5. PENALTIES:</b>
                    In the event that a team is unable to participate in a league match. A penalty of R960.00 will be charged to the
                    teams account for each match missed.
                </p>

                <p>
