                    Motion Inc. Sports is not by any means responsible for any injuries that may occur during a game neither can
                    Motion Inc. Sports be held accountable for any injuries sustain within the premisis. First Aid Kits will be available.
                </p>

                <p>
                    <b>7. COMPLAINTS:</b>
                    Should an applicant have cause to make a complaint about any aspect of Motion Inc. Sports facilities or the of service
                    provided by the referee they should address their concerns to Adminstartion.

                </p>

                <p>
                    <b>8. GENERAL:</b>
                    Motion inc. Sports must be notified immediately of any significant change in the team list. Once a team is registered
                    to the league, hence the team can not be removed.
                </p>

